Warrior of the 28th Season
<BR>
Valeer Shadowsbaine
Shadow Knight of the 41st Season (WOW IT MOVED!!!!)</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/uquemnwyndrunner.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Quemn Wyndrunner</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(9/6/00 4:23:09 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Bard 1HB question</span><hr size=1> if you ever use a staff of writhing as a bard you're retarded, it takes away from our primary stat CHA! never, ever, ever use a staff of writhing as a bard!<br>
