52 Bard <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/ubrinklith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brinklith</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(9/7/00 12:10:14 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/legendward/brink.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Bard 1HB question</span><hr size=1> I agree that the CHA penalty is awful with the ugly stick, but if you're using weapons and _not_ using your CHA (Enchanter already in group, eg) why not use it? <p><b>Brinklith Rioghbhardan</b> - Jester of Avalon<br>
